metadata.name: CTKxBGG - Pin 3% | #1
metadata.description: Holders of "Carry The Key - Official" Keys receive these airdrops as an owner incentive. If licensed, these packages pay out royalties in ETH to the Holders ETH wallet. Look for a "Licensed" trait to know if the NFT is currently Licensed and paying out! (Share percentages are on the NFTs and add up. i.e., (2) NFTs with 3% share = 6% total.)
